WEBVTT

00:08:28.257 --> 00:08:31.093
because that would
certainly lead to chaos.

00:08:31.704 --> 00:08:36.482
So we need alignment and autonomy
at the same time,

00:08:36.506 --> 00:08:38.193
just like a flock of birds.

00:08:39.594 --> 00:08:41.871
In an organizational setting,

00:08:41.895 --> 00:08:43.665
this requires new behaviors,

00:08:43.689 --> 00:08:45.795
and with each new behavior,

00:08:45.819 --> 00:08:48.640
there is giving up
on something old as well.

00:08:49.751 --> 00:08:53.753
Leaders have to make sure
that everyone in the organization

00:08:53.777 --> 00:08:56.945
is aligned around
the overall purpose -- the why --

00:08:56.969 --> 00:08:59.257
and the overall priorities -- the what.

00:08:59.281 --> 00:09:03.089
But then they have to let go
and trust their teams